[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "えっ、参加資格が「愛し合う者同士」……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ええ。ホルハーツ鳥のメスを捕まえるのは\nとても困難を極めるでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ですが、愛し合う者同士で協力すれば……\n大きな愛があればどんな困難にも打ち勝てるはず！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そう！　愛はすべてに勝るのですから！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ええっ！　そ、そんな参加資格、急に言われても……\nどうしよう、レスナちゃん、ヨハナ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "大きな愛を見せるって、そういうことかよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うわー、ここまで徹底してるとは……\nアタシたち、どうする？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様と愛し合う日が、来たわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そうだわね。って、ちょいと待たんかい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "愛し合うってのはよく分からないけど……\n家族愛なら負けないわよ。ね、ランツェ、フロッケ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "お、おうとも！\nこれが愛じゃねえならなんだってんだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "はい！　この愛の大きさは誰にも負けません！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……素晴らしい！　家族愛も立派な愛の形です。\n参加、認めましょう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "なるほど、なるほど。それでいいんですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "じゃあ、アタシたちは友愛！　\nレスナちゃんのこともヨハナのことも、大好きだし！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それじゃあ、アタシたちは姉妹愛だね、ベップ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ええ。島中のみんなに見せつけてやるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "友愛、姉妹愛、家族愛――どれも素晴らしい愛です。\n皆さん、参加資格ありと認めます！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（本当はもう一人、家族はいるのですが……\n　ハイディさん、今は何をしているのでしょうか？）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "大変お待たせいたしました！\nそれでは、「愛のレース」を開始します！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "運営スタッフ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ホルハーツ鳥のメスを見つけ出し、\n愛の力を示してください！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "いよいよ始まるね！\nレスナちゃん、ヨハナ、準備はいい？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、頑張ろうね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ベップ、気合入れていくよ！　\n姉妹の底力、舐めんじゃねえっての！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "もちろん、姉様。負けないわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "フロッケ、ランツェ、行くわよ。\n家族の絆、見せつけてやろうじゃない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おう、任せとけ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "はい、ヴァレリアさん、ランツェさん。\n頑張りましょう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]